high_descs: Turn around and move to the other room with the blue couch.
Pick up the newspaper from the blue chair.
Hold the newspaper and turn to the right then the left and face the blue chair on the left.
Place the newspaper on the blue ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Move the newspaper from the chair to ottoman.

high_descs: Walk over to the purple chair behind you.
Pick up the newspaper off of the seat of the purple chair.
Walk over to the front of the foot stool that is in front of the purple chair.
Place the newspaper on the right side of the foot stool.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper to a foot stool.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the purple chair with the newspaper on it.
Pick the newspaper up from the chair.
Turn to the right and then the left to face the ottoman.
Put the newspaper down on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Put a newspaper on an ottoman.
